{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'There are still quite a few hostile bionics around.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "There aren't as many as before. New Murmansk should become safer now that Amberia has been silenced.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Speaking of, Commandant. You and Rosetta completed the mission together, huh. We were doing data collection for Lucia at the time.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Thankfully, you completed the mission in one piece.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "...I'm glad that everyone came back alive.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Well, of course. This isn't our commandant's first time in battle.", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory94.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'But back on to Amberia... What is she anyway?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'She was a monster born out of sin.', 3: '24'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'What the commandant means is, Amberia was designed by technicians with distorted obsessions.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Even just going through the video records and files afterwards, I can't help but feel... a shiver run down my spine.", 4: '2'}
{2: "What's the matter?", 3: '33'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Oh, it's nothing. It just makes me kinda... sad.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Humanity brought about the tragedy of Amberia, and we're here to protect humanity...", 4: '1'}
{3: "Liv looks at you blankly. Liv's Levi-Guns seem a little wobbly in the air."}
{2: "We'll change the world for the better.", 3: '37'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "...Let's keep going.", 4: '1'}
